<h1 class="main-text" style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:rgb(28,39,102);">Work with foster youth: <br><br>become a Foster Skills Associate!</h1>
<img class="main-image" style="float:right;margin-left:15px;margin-bottom:15px;margin-top:10px;margin-right:8px;" src="http://www.fosterskills.org/images/work_with_youth_main-image.jpg" alt="placeholder">

<h2 class="main-text">Position Overview</h2>
<p class="main-text">Foster Skills seeks a mature college or graduate student for an internship (12-15 hours/week). This is an unpaid internship; however, we will work with you to receive school credit or recommendations. To apply, please email your resume and short paragraph stating your interest to info@fosterskills.org.<br><br>
We are interested in working around your interests and talents, but some possible duties include: supporting a young person through an ongoing Associate relationship, serving as a positive role model and friend, implementing the foster skills curriculum, and managing group mentoring sessions.
</p>
